		<a href="http://werblog.com/2003/11/ntia-spectrum-event/" title="NTIA spectrum event" rel="bookmark">NTIA spectrum event</a>
		
	</h2>

	
	
	<div class="post-bodycopy cf">
	
		<div class="post-date">		
			<p class="post-month">Nov</p>
			<p class="post-day">21</p>
			<p class="post-year">2003</p>				
		</div>

		The National Telecommunications and Information Administration, which managed government spectrum, is holding a forum on spectrum policy on December 9, with other events planned in January and February.&nbsp; This is part of the Bush Administration&#8217;s spectrum task force initiative, launched in June.
		
	</div>

